content:
Hi everyone,
I am organising an online reading seminar this term with the goal of understanding the cohesive framework of TED (Twisted Equivariant Differential) K-theory for Topological Quantum computation and Anyonic Defect branes. If anyone is interested, you are welcome to participate.

Here's the link to the website.

We'll be using Discord for the seminar, so feel free to DM in case you are interested.
